quran[86]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Okhururalana khushina shiabarebananga
  78,2,Okhurulana nende amacheni amakhongo
  78,3,Kalia akabawukhanangamwo
  78,4,"Tawe lekha butswa, ahambi hano baletsa okhumanya"
  78,5,"Mana Khandi tawe lekha butswa, ahambi hano baletsa okhumanya"
  78,6,Shikhwakhola liloba okhuba shinga obulili
  78,7,Ne tsingulu okhuba tsisiilo
  78,8,Ne ni khubaloonga tsimbia tsibili (eshisatsa neshikhasi)
  78,9,Ne nikhukhola okhukona khwenyu okhuba okhuwuluukha
  78,10,Ne nikhukhola eshilo okhuba eshifwalo
  78,11,"Ne\tnikhukhola\teshitere\tokhuba shiokhukhalabanila obulamu"
  78,12,Ne nikhumbakha hekulu wenyu amakulu saba aka amani
  78,13,Ne nikhukasia itaa yobulafu nende obubafu
  78,14,Ne nikhwishia amatsi karulanga bwangu okhurula mumaleesi
  78,15,kachila khurusie khuko imele nende emimela
  78,16,Nende emikunda chiemisala chiatilana
  78,17,Toto inyanga yobwaukhasi yarebwaho khubise
  78,18,"Inyanga yolwika lulikhupwa, nanyu muliitsa mumikanda"
  78,19,Ne likulu liliikulwa liaba shinga emiliango
  78,20,Ne tsingulu tsilisiulwa tsiaba shinga amaweruweru
  78,21,Toto Jahanamu iliindanga
  78,22,Niyo eshimenyo shia Abakhayi
  78,23,Balimenyamwo tsinyanga netsinyanga
  78,24,Shibalipilamwo shiosi shiosi eshinyifu nohomba eshinywebwa tawe
  78,25,Halali amatsi kayile nende amafila
  78,26,Nomurungo kubayela
  78,27,Toto bo Shibasubilanga mbu khuliba nende inyanga yemikabo tawe
  78,28,Ne nibayingana muno khubimanyisio biefu
  78,29,"Nebuli\teshindu\tkhwatililila mubuhandiche"
  78,30,Kho mupile! Shikhubameta shiosi shiosi tawe halali eshinyasio
  78,31,toto abaria Nyasaye nibo balihonokokha
  78,32,(balinyoola) emekunda nende tsizabibu
  78,33,Nende abakhana bayelana ninabo
  78,34,Nende tsigilasi tsitsule (ebinywebwa ebilayi)
  78,35,Shibaliwulilamwo obusilu nohomba amayinji tawe
  78,36,Omurungo ukhurula Khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi Omurungo kuyela
  78,37,Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo nende biosi bilimwo Omunji wetsimbabaasi shibalilomaloma imbeli wuwe tawe
  78,38,"Inyanga ya Roho (Jibreel) alisinjila nende Abamalaika khulunyaali. Shalilomaloma yesiyesi tawe okhuyiniakhwo ulia ulifuchililwa nende Nyasaye wetsimbabaasi, ne aliboola obulaamba bwonyene"
  78,39,Eyo niyo inyanga yatoto. Ne owenya atile injila akalushile Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi
  78,40,"Toto efwe khubekanyisilia eshinyasio shili ahambi okhuula. Inyanga ya Omundu alilola kayakhola omwene. Ne Omukhayi aliboola mbu: “manyanga ndakhabeele liloba!”"
  79,1,Nditsuba Khubamalaika bakhunyulanga (emioyo cha bakhayi) nende amaani
  79,2,Nende balia barusinjia (emioyo chiabasuubili) kaala
  79,3,Nende balia bakulukhanga mwikulu bukulukha
  79,4,Nende balia bashilananga tsimbilo (nende emioyo chiabasuubili okhuyila mwikulu)
  79,5,"Nende balia bakaasinjia amakhuwa. (emioyo emibii nichinyoola eshinyasio, ne emilayi nichisangaasibwa)"
  79,6,Inyanga yolwika lulikhupwa lweyimbeli (lulirenjia buli eshindu)
  79,7,Ne ulwika lundi lulilondakhwo
  79,8,Inyanga eyo emioyo chilirengarenga khuburi
  79,9,Tsimoni tsiachio tsilikhookha. (tsilihenga hasi)
  79,10,"(Abakhayi) baboolanga mbu: “khulikalusibwa toto shinga khwali?” (Khulilamusibwa)"
  79,11,Olwakhuliba ebikumba bibulungukha
  79,12,"Baboola mbu: “okhukalusibwa okho nikhweshikhaya (khwifwe! )”"
  79,13,Kho toto okhulamusibwa okho ni oluyoka lulala lwonyene
  79,14,hawo na hawo buli eshiloonje shiliba mushikuri eshiya
  79,15,Koo! lwakhuulilakhwo Olukano lwa Musa
  79,16,Olwa Nyasaye wuwe yamulanga mulitwoma lio luyali lia T’uwaa
  79,17,"Tsia ewa Firauni, toto ye yaburirira"
  79,18,"Umuboolele mbu: “Koo ochama okhuba Omutswenufu?”"
  79,19,Ekhwimilile khu Nyasaye wo onyoole okhumuria
  79,20,Mana namwenchesia ebimanyisio ebikhongo
  79,21,Ne naloba nakhaila elala
  79,22,"Khandi nakalukha inyuma, nakhola eshinani. (Okhukania Abandu balafuchilila Musa tawe)"
  79,23,Nakhung’asia Abandu nalaanga
  79,24,"Naboola mbu: “nesie Nyasaye wenyu Omukhongo.”"
  79,25,Kho Omulonji namutila namuhelesia eshinyasio khukayaboola kokhumalilikha (nesie Nyasaye wenyue omukhongo) nende kayaranjilila (Abulaho Nyasaye wundi owulali esie)
  79,26,toto esho neshimanyisio khubalia baria Nyasaye
  79,27,Koo! Nobutinyu okhuloonga enywe nohomba likulu? Ye niye waliumbakha
  79,28,"yalichingula, nalikasia obulayi"
  79,29,"Ne nara eshilima mushilo shiayio, ne nayiniamwo eshitere"
  79,30,Akhurula awo nakwalasia liloba
  79,31,Narusiamwo amatsikayio nende emimela
  79,32,Ne nabuusia tsingulu
  79,33,Khubukhala bwenyu nende ibiayo bienyu
  79,34,Olwamatinyu amakhongo kaliula
  79,35,Inyanga yomundu aliitsulila kayakhola
  79,36,ne jahanamu ilisitibwa khu ulola
  79,37,ne ulia waburirira mubufuru
  79,38,mana nachama muno ubulamu bweshialo
  79,39,toto jahanamu neshimenyo shishie
  79,40,"Ne ulia waria okhwema imbeli Wa Nyasaye wuwe , nakaania omwoyo kukwe obwikombi"
  79,41,Toto oyo Mwikulu nishiliba eshimenyo shishie
  79,42,Bakhurebanga ebise bieyindukho biliba lina
  79,43,Oli nashina ewe wakhanyala okhuyirumbula
  79,44,Obumalilishi bweyinyanga eyo buli khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi
  79,45,Toto ewe oli butswa Omwikanyilisi khu ulia owaria inyanga eyo
  79,46,"Olwa baliyilola inyanga eyo, balikaala mbu shibamenya khwo (khushialo) tawe halali ingolobe ndala nohomba eshitere shiayo"